quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,79,"Ngwamba! Uwwe chitulembe yajukuŵecheta, ni tuchin’jonjechesya ndaŵi jelewu nnope jailagasyo."
  19,80,"Ni tuchintawalila (pajuchiwapo) yosope yajukwambayo (chipanje ni ŵanache ŵakweo), ni juchituichilila (ku Kiyama) juli jikajikape."
  19,81,"Eti ŵanganyao alitendele milungu jinepe kunneka Allah, kuti jape ŵanganyao machili ni uchimbichimbi."
  20,61,"Musa jwasalile ŵanganyao kuti: “Kutapana kwenu ŵanyamwe! Ngasimunsepelela Allah unami, atakwika mwanteketulenye ni ilagasyo, soni pamasile paajonasiche mundu jwaasepelele unami.”"
  20,62,"Basi (asaŵi) ŵaakanganile chilikati chao pa ichindu yao (yakwamba Musa ni nkulugwe), ni ŵasongonelene mwantemela."
  20,63,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite (mukusongonelana mwao): “Chisimu ŵanyaŵatu asaŵi (ŵamanye chenene), ni usaŵi waowo akusaka kuti ankoposye jenumanja m’chilambo mwenu, ni kumasya nyendele jenu jajili jambone nnope.”"
  21,37,"Mundu jugumbidwe kuŵa jwakupupuluma. Sampano chinannosye ŵanganyammwe ilosyo Yangu (yakaiche ka ipotesi), basi ngasimunyanguya."
  21,38,"(Achimakafili) ni akasatiji: “Ana chele chilangachi chiyiche chakachi nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona?”"
  21,39,"Ingaŵe kuti akumanyilila aŵala ŵakanile ndema jatachitenda ngauchiga Moto kungope kwao, namuno kunyuma kwao (nganganaŵecheta yalakweyo), soni ŵanganyao ngasaŵa ŵakamuchisyidwa."
  22,13,"Jukasaŵaŵendaga aŵala ŵagali masausyo gao gakuŵandichila nnope kulekangana ni ikamuchisyo yao, kaje kusakala nnope kaligoselo kakwe, soni kaje kusakala nnope nsyoŵe jwakwe!"
  22,14,"Chisimu Allah tachajinjisya aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima sulo cha pasi pakwe. Chisimu Allah akasatendaga yaakusaka."
  22,15,"Jwalijose jwaakuŵa nkuganichisya yanti Allah nganaŵa ankamuchisye (Muhammadi ﷺ) paduniya ni ku Akhera, basi akoleche lukonji kunsakasa kaneko ni alitaŵilile, ni alole kuti ana chitagu chakwecho chichityosye yaikumpikasya ntimayo (ana kuliulaga kwakweko chikutendekasye kuti Usilamu ukajenela)?"